  "texts": [
    "The level of satisfaction of nursing students in perceived ease of use, credibility, social influence, and privacy and security was relatively equal across the sex groups (i.e., male and female).",
    "However, in terms of usefulness, this study found out that female students were highly satisfied (𝑥̅ =4.013) of the usefulness of ChatGPT in learning.",
    "This perception significantly differed (t=2.239; σ=0.027) compared to male students (𝑥̅ =3.675).",
